{"tid":1956670,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"朱凱廸 : 防暴訓練不戴罩 缺泛防疫常識累人累己","createTime":"2020-04-03T10:42:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T10:00:50.000Z","uid":21470,"like":217,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"50d11d58ae95c90433b2ef3a14c9b86f96201509","tid":1956670,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"八鄉朱凱廸 Chu Hoi Dick <br />\n<br />\n【防暴唔戴罩 不怕3萬Thanks？】<br />\n<br />\n警察如今除了高於法律，行私刑冇後果，似乎連衛生防疫常識也想超越埋。<br />\n香港三月中武肺疫情再起，每天數十宗確診個案，但一批為數五十人的防暴警察上星期三和四（3月25及26日）在元朗牛潭尾濾水廠訓練期間，居然全程零口罩密切接觸。<br />\n<br />\n提供照片的X君表示，防暴警每次訓練歷時個多小時，由早上十點多至中午十二點：「佢地不但冇戴口罩，而且不停大聲叫囂，除下頭盔時雙手不停觸摸面部，衛生意識非常差劣！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然網上很多「三萬thanks」呼聲，但X君仍然希望提醒警察，任何時間都要戴上合規格的外科口罩，以免累人累己。<br />\n<br />\n不過，從《開心字典》學講野、練成「永不犯錯」神功的PK鄧可能會解釋，由於疫情持續，警察正訓練不戴口罩而防病毒，這個post只是反對派針對警察的又一例證。<br />\n#牛潭尾濾水廠 #防暴訓練唔戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chuhoidick/posts/2875136475885591\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchuhoidick%2Fposts%2F2875136475885591&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=8106cdcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chuhoidick/posts/2875136475885591</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sF3wuPq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsF3wuPq.jpg&h=68be5110&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w20629t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw20629t.jpg&h=af41f984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnvSef8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnvSef8.jpg&h=4f3d20a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44ea0549bfd6b689c1910dd9f4f680626b43ec4b","tid":1956670,"uid":151313,"like":429,"dislike":3,"score":426,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:44:55.000Z","msg":"唔戴咪幾好 一陣一人感染 咪可以成隊攬炒"},{"pid":"5fb63eb1960563bfc8b96786ebe710cec913bd39","tid":1956670,"uid":123053,"like":12